Build instructions:
===================

$ mkdir ~/var-imx-yocto-krogoth-jig
$ cd ~/var-imx-yocto-krogoth-jig
$ repo init -u git://git.freescale.com/imx/fsl-arm-yocto-bsp.git -b imx-4.1-krogoth
$ repo sync -j8
$ cd ~/var-imx-yocto-krogoth-jig/sources
$ git clone https://github.com/varjig/meta-variscite-imx-jig.git -b imx6ul-Krogoth-imx-4.1.15-var01
$ cp meta-variscite-imx-jig/scripts/var-setup-release.sh ../

$ cd ~/var-imx-yocto-krogoth-jig
$ MACHINE=imx6ul-var-dart DISTRO=fsl-imx-fb source var-setup-release.sh -b build_fb
$ bitbake core-image-minimal

To rebuild the images after a change:
========================================
$ bitbake -c cleansstate linux-variscite u-boot-variscite u-boot-fw-utils wpa-supplicant-wl18xx
$ bitbake -c cleanall core-image-minimal
$ bitbake core-image-minimal

To create an SD Card from the images run:
========================================
$ sudo ../sources/meta-variscite-imx-jig/scripts/var_mk_yocto_sdcard/jig-create-sdcard.sh /dev/sdg

To create USB from the images run:
========================================
$ sudo ../sources/meta-variscite-imx-jig/scripts/var_mk_yocto_sdcard/jig-create-usb.sh /dev/sdh
